<Layout title="What Are Satoshis? The Smallest Unit of Bitcoin Explained" description="Learn what satoshis are, how they relate to Bitcoin, and why this tiny unit matters for everyday crypto transactions." keywords="satoshis, what is a satoshi, smallest bitcoin unit, sats, bitcoin denominations, bitcoin fractions, crypto units">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <article class="prose dark:prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6 not-prose">
